“Donald Trump's illegal war in Iran has had a direct impact on California housing prices, causing high costs to rise even higher.

He's spent billions of our taxpayer dollars bombing the Middle East while our affordability crisis keeps spiraling out of control.”

We endorse Melat Kiros for Congress in Colorado’s 1st District!

@melatkirosco.bsky.social is running on Medicare for All, Housing First, and universal childcare.

In Denver, where rising costs are pushing folks to the brink, she’s organizing for real solutions that meet the scale of the crisis.
